Subject: The Dark Web Big Three
Description: Get and introduction to the big three in censorship-resistant communication, TOR, I2P and freenet and learn how they work and some of the options they have available.  Speakers include:Pat Baker - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Tor: what is it and is it an onion?
Description: A general background of TOR, the onion router. Includes discussion on how to install it and some of the options to create your own dark web sites.  Speakers include:Pat Baker - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes
